parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description: The name of the namespace that you specify when you call the [CreatevNamespace](~~2850317~~) operation.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number. The product of PageNumber and PageSize cannot exceed 50,000.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Default value: 50. Maximum value: 100.
